    "name": "Pelican Harbor",
    "steam_appid": 3001740,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/51c04fecdbf04cb03ce056b936ad5913.avif?t=1746268177\" width=800 height=261 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes! Pelican Harbor reimagines the way Rhythm Games work.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You choose your favorite music by simply listening to it<strong>.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>All you need is your ears and a sense of rhythm!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1) You mimic the beat of a song</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2) The game calculates its BPM</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3) You start fishing and the game generates different maps each time!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/c515d5e32eaa214f9bebec12418611c2.poster.avif?t=1746268177\" width=600 height=164 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/c515d5e32eaa214f9bebec12418611c2.webm?t=1746268177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/c515d5e32eaa214f9bebec12418611c2.mp4?t=1746268177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leveling, Runes &amp; Skills</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/90597b7805e7fc939d93201fff268f1b.webp?t=1746268177\" width=157 height=14 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn experience points by catching or filleting fish, completing quests and burning materials. Upgrade specific skills and unlock runes which add small rhythm variations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rarities of Islands, Fish &amp; Fish Bait</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/838383db1447c48fd6baa78be3d5b3a8.webp?t=1746268177\" width=291 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Islands, fish and fish bait are categorized by them. You start on an ordinary island with the goal to buy more rare islands. Your island's rarity sets the max. rarity of fish you can catch.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Filleting Fish &amp; Fish Bait</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/6f2f4a14277bbbfac37458f679182fcb.webp?t=1746268177\" width=151 height=19 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Either sell fish to gain Pico or fillet your fish for a chance of obtaining fish bait of the next higher rarity. Fishing with bait ensures a 50% catch rate of fish from this rarity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/49767180159f52adc541b8830558bcf0.poster.avif?t=1746268177\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/49767180159f52adc541b8830558bcf0.webm?t=1746268177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/49767180159f52adc541b8830558bcf0.mp4?t=1746268177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Islands, Terraforming, Paths &amp; Placeable Objects</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Islands are procedurally generated. You can terraform everything above sand level and create paths. Place objects like your camp or lighthouse freely to customize your island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >High Quality</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Built from scratch with a custom engine, Pelican Harbor excels in high performance and smooth gameplay, even on low-end systems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/1292bf66c4a683c107ef814ede9e1dde.poster.avif?t=1746268177\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/1292bf66c4a683c107ef814ede9e1dde.webm?t=1746268177\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001740/extras/1292bf66c4a683c107ef814ede9e1dde.mp4?t=1746268177\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >... and more Features!</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Co-op with up to 4 Friends</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traveling NPCs</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sell Fish or buy Tools, Accessories &amp; entire Islands</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pelican Customization</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face, Height, Body- &amp; Eye Color, Backpack- &amp; Hat Accessories</p></li></ul></li></ul>",
